==Trivia==
* Cave kraken use the same model as the [[Sea Troll Queen]] but it is recoloured and resized.
* Cave kraken and their boss variant are similar to ''RuneScape''<nowiki/>'s {{RSL|Strykewyrm}}s, which can only be attacked while on a Slayer task and must be disturbed to fight.
* The cave kraken had a festive override wearing a [[santa hat]] during the [[2016 Christmas event/Gallery|2016]], [[2017 Christmas event/Gallery|2017]], [[2018 Christmas event/Gallery|2018]], and [[2019 Christmas event/Gallery|2019]] Christmas events. Both the NPC and skill guide icon had the override.

